    "description": "Hottolink, Inc. provides social media marketing support that collects, analyzes, and utilizes social big data in Japan. The company offers Social Network Service marketing support, SNS operation consulting, and SNS analysis tools. It also provides Web3 related business, including sale of rights to access data from various SNS. In addition, the company offers Instagram and X marketing support, influencer marketing support, post campaign, programmatic social media advertising, fasme content marketing and inbound support, and creative production. Further, it provides hashpick, an analysis tool for Instagram marketing; and DarkOwl, a cybersecurity platform for rapid detection of corporate data breaches. Additionally, the company engages in the investment management business activities. Hottolink, Inc. was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
